Package: PosPredictor
Title: Posterior Probability of Success for OS Using PFS as Surrogate
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for computing the posterior Probability of
    Success (PoS) using PFS log(HR) to predict OS log(HR) via a hierarchical
    random-effects meta-analytic model. Supports both closed-form conjugate
    multivariate-normal solutions and full Bayesian MCMC via Stan.
